 SUPERUSER DO !! aka. SUDO**
 first install sudo before we run more programs & tools
 SUDO not full work on Magisk !! Root your smartphone with SuperSU
 
follow the next steps for SUDO**
 >Copy&Past:

termux-setup-storage

apt update && apt upgrade

apt install git

pkg install ncurses-utils

git clone https://github.com/GottModusTermux/GodToolsTermux.git && cd GodToolsTermux/sudo

apt install fish && fish

cat sudo > /data/data/com.termux/files/usr/bin/sudo

chmod 700 /data/data/com.termux/files/usr/bin/sudo 

exit

sudo

